<style>
@page {
  margin: 10px 20px 30px 20px;
}

@media print {
  .print-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 8px;
    padding-bottom: 20mm; /* damit nix abgeschnitten wird */
  }

  .img {
  break-inside: avoid;
}
  
  .print-item {
    break-inside: avoid;
    page-break-inside: avoid;
    background: #fff;
  }

  /* <<< Hier kommt die Klasse für erzwungenen Seitenumbruch >>> */
  .page-break {
    break-before: page; /* moderne Schreibweise */
    /* fallback: page-break-before: always; */
  }
}
</style>

const timestamp = context.workflow['124c175e-8a26-432f-80e8-309dc8fd0174'].result

const pdf_name = context.workflow['8a70fa07-ea0d-4f05-818b-7d87e9eb6014'].result

const { data, error } = await wwLib.wwPlugins.supabaseAuth.publicInstance
  .storage
  .from('pdf_print')
  .createSignedUploadUrl(user_id + '/'+ timestamp+'/'+ pdf_name)

  return data
